snippet.title: Planet Explorers Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Ready to create your own adventure in Planet Explorers? 
Join the Beta on Steam now, explore the world and craft your own story in this unique sandbox experience: http://store.steampowered.com/app/237870/

Follow Pathea Gamers, creators of Planet Explorers, on:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PatheaGames
Facebook: www.facebook.com/PatheaGames/
